 Understanding Backend Concepts

This repository serves as a portfolio and learning resource, documenting key concepts and practical implementations required for modern Web 2 backend development.

Each major concept is isolated in its own folder for easy review and testing.

Concepts Covered

Folder

Topic

Key Takeaways

01_password_hashing

Password Hashing (bcrypt)

Demonstrates the correct usage of salt generation and the critical difference between bcrypt.hashpw() and bcrypt.checkpw().
